    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Poisonous frogs are a bright green color, with additional bright yellow, red, or blue markings. They are just over a foot long and weigh 10 pounds. The poison of poisonous frogs is often gathered by primitive tribes and used to coat darts and arrows for hunting.<br/><br/>You can make a larger poison frog either by applying the giant simple template or by giving a normal giant frog a poison frog\u2019s venomous bite."
        }
    ],
